spec_data.Name: perl-Session-Storage-Secure
spec_data.Description:
This module implements a secure way to encode session data. It is primarily
intended for storing session data in browser cookies, but could be used
with other back-end storage where security of stored session data is
important.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 03:47:26 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Encrypted, expiring, compressed, serialized session data with integrity
